# ng-mfe-hub — Angular Micro-Frontend Hub

## Project Identity

Nx 22.5 monorepo for an Angular micro-frontend architecture using **Dynamic Module Federation**.
Shell (host) app orchestrates 6 remote MFE apps, each independently deployable.

## Tech Stack

- **Framework**: Angular 21+ (standalone components, signals, new control flow)
- **Monorepo**: Nx 22.5 (`nx.json`, per-project `project.json`)
- **MFE**: Dynamic Module Federation via `@nx/angular` + Webpack
- **UI Components**: ng-bootstrap (`@ng-bootstrap/ng-bootstrap`)
- **Styling**: Bootstrap 5 (utility-first, no jQuery) + shared SCSS in `libs/shared/styles`
- **Icons**: Themify Icons

