## 3-Level Shared Hierarchy

| Level | Location | Scope | Example |
|-------|----------|-------|---------|
| Global | `libs/shared/*` | All apps | `@ng-mfe-hub/ui` |
| App | `libs/<app>/*` | Single app + its features | `@ng-mfe-hub/dashboard-ui` |
| Feature | `libs/<app>/feature-*` | Single feature, lazy-loaded | `@ng-mfe-hub/dashboard-feature-users` |

## Smart / Dumb Component Pattern

- **Smart** (`containers/`): inject services, manage signals, pass data down
- **Dumb** (`components/`): pure `input()`/`output()`, no injected services, `OnPush`

## Key Commands

| Task | Command |
|------|---------|
| Serve everything | `nx serve shell` |
| Serve single remote | `nx serve dashboard` |
| Build app | `nx build shell` |
| Test project | `nx test dashboard-feature-users` |
| Lint project | `nx lint shell` |
| Affected only | `nx affected -t build,test,lint` |
| Generate lib | `nx g @nx/angular:lib libs/<scope>/<name> --name=<scope>-<name>` |
| Generate component | `nx g @nx/angular:component --path=libs/.../path` |

## Module Boundaries (Nx Tags)

- **scope**: `shared`, `shell`, `dashboard`, `profile`, `lab`, `theme`, `demos`
- **type**: `app`, `feature`, `ui`, `data-access`, `util`, `styles`
- `scope:shared` — importable by everyone
- `scope:<app>` — only importable within that app and its libs
- `type:feature` — cannot import other features
- `type:ui` — cannot import features or data-access
- `type:util` — leaf node, no upward dependencies
